{
  "stem": "20021.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Later on, I read an editorial in the Budapest paper which was maybe like in the months of January, where the editor of that paper-- which was in German, but it was one of the most important papers in-- in Budapest-- appealed to the population to go out of their way, and to the Budapest government, to help refugees and other people.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In order so that after the war, we can claim, you know, that we helped rather than, you know, pay for our sins which we did by cooperating with Germany officially.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Unfortunately, very quickly after that, Eichmann arrived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "OK, now, while I was in jail, there was a Polish person there who was caught in Yugoslavia on the border between Hungary and Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was caught with very incriminating photos documenting the fact that he worked for the British CID, which is the British CIA, British intelligence service.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he came back to the cell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Unlike me and my father, he was beaten severely.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was beaten on his feet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they insisted-- and it wasn't that same judge.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was another guy who interrogated him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they insisted on him confessing that he is a spy for the British.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he told me that he is finished, that he'll probably they'll kill him right there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he'll finish his life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I really pity on him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I, at that point, uncovered already a weakness in the system, where I felt that the person could escape their whole system.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The weakness was very simple.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They had a system where people who came to visit prisoners, families who came to visit prisoners, would come to the prison, register themselves in the book, give a name.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
